WEBVTT

00:00:01.329 --> 00:00:05.717
The shocking police crackdown
on protestors in Ferguson, Missouri,

00:00:05.717 --> 00:00:08.729
in the wake of the police 
shooting of Michael Brown,

00:00:08.729 --> 00:00:12.952
underscored the extent to which advanced
military weapons and equipment,

00:00:12.952 --> 00:00:14.684
designed for the battlefield,

00:00:14.684 --> 00:00:15.993
are making their way

00:00:15.993 --> 00:00:19.874
to small-town police departments
across the United States.

00:00:20.514 --> 00:00:22.500
Although much tougher to observe,

00:00:22.500 --> 00:00:26.047
this same thing is happening 
with surveillance equipment.

00:00:26.047 --> 00:00:28.707
NSA-style mass 
surveillance is enabling

00:00:28.707 --> 00:00:31.665
local police departments 
to gather vast quantities